1
00:01:24,120 --> 00:01:24,599
It's all taken care of.

2
00:01:27,959 --> 00:01:28,400
Let's go.

3
00:01:29,599 --> 00:01:30,000
Go.

4
00:01:31,879 --> 00:01:32,280
Move.

5
00:01:44,959 --> 00:01:45,760
Monkey's been buried.

6
00:01:53,239 --> 00:01:53,920
Your medicine.

7
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:54,760
The upgraded version.

8
00:02:01,920 --> 00:02:03,560
The medicine you give me is always so bitter.

9
00:02:07,959 --> 00:02:09,199
Didn't Qiu Ge give you some candy?

10
00:02:09,879 --> 00:02:10,400
Take them together.

11
00:02:27,719 --> 00:02:28,599
In all of Black Street,

12
00:02:28,879 --> 00:02:30,319
you're the only one who dares eat Qiu Ge's candy.

13
00:02:32,240 --> 00:02:33,800
Sister Qiu Ge is really nice.

14
00:02:51,520 --> 00:02:52,280
You know what?

15
00:02:52,800 --> 00:02:54,120
In all of Shanhai City,

16
00:02:55,039 --> 00:02:57,479
you matter the most to me.

17
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:00,240
Have a seat.

18
00:03:01,159 --> 00:03:01,639
Okay.

19
00:03:04,840 --> 00:03:05,439
Would you like some coffee?

20
00:03:07,000 --> 00:03:07,560
Sure.

21
00:03:08,039 --> 00:03:10,439
The best coffee in Qiushui City.

22
00:03:18,520 --> 00:03:19,319
From Qiushui.

23
00:03:22,759 --> 00:03:23,599
Go brew some.

24
00:03:26,800 --> 00:03:27,560
Are you sure?

25
00:03:28,840 --> 00:03:29,639
Of course.

26
00:03:30,199 --> 00:03:31,280
It's just a cup of coffee.

27
00:03:43,599 --> 00:03:44,759
Careful, it's hot.

28
00:03:45,400 --> 00:03:46,080
Drink it slowly.

29
00:03:50,840 --> 00:03:51,560
I think

30
00:03:52,039 --> 00:03:53,520
you still need more experience.

31
00:03:54,960 --> 00:03:57,000
Take this operation, for example.

32
00:03:58,280 --> 00:04:00,080
Qiushui coffee

33
00:04:00,199 --> 00:04:01,319
has always been rich and smooth.

34
00:04:01,919 --> 00:04:04,080
Yours tastes a bit different

35
00:04:04,240 --> 00:04:05,039
from what I usually drink.

36
00:04:06,599 --> 00:04:07,639
It's a little sour.

37
00:04:10,960 --> 00:04:12,520
Could it be expired?

38
00:04:14,560 --> 00:04:16,560
Let's skip this topic

39
00:04:17,079 --> 00:04:18,120
and talk about Black Street.

40
00:04:19,000 --> 00:04:19,759
I've decided

41
00:04:19,879 --> 00:04:22,000
to send you to Black Street for a while.

42
00:04:22,199 --> 00:04:22,800
I believe

43
00:04:23,160 --> 00:04:24,360
you'll gain a lot

44
00:04:24,519 --> 00:04:25,839
from your time on Black Street.

45
00:04:26,279 --> 00:04:27,000
In one month,

46
00:04:27,360 --> 00:04:28,360
come back and report to me.

47
00:04:29,199 --> 00:04:29,920
By then,

48
00:04:30,160 --> 00:04:32,040
you'll surely be the most capable

49
00:04:32,279 --> 00:04:33,480
captain in the Celestial Vanguard.

50
00:04:33,879 --> 00:04:34,519
Are you confident?

51
00:04:34,680 --> 00:04:35,720
I'll definitely do my best.

52
00:04:35,720 --> 00:04:36,319
Good.

53
00:04:36,839 --> 00:04:38,600
Then I hope on Black Street,

54
00:04:38,680 --> 00:04:40,000
you'll bring out the Celestial Vanguard's—

55
00:04:40,399 --> 00:04:42,319
Do you have a restroom?

56
00:04:42,680 --> 00:04:43,959
A... a restroom?

57
00:04:43,959 --> 00:04:45,480
I... excuse me for a moment.

58
00:04:45,560 --> 00:04:45,920
What the—

59
00:05:00,319 --> 00:05:01,160
A young man's heart

60
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:02,360
can surpass even the immortals,

61
00:05:03,120 --> 00:05:04,759
let alone a mere Black Street.

62
00:05:05,560 --> 00:05:06,160
My future

63
00:05:06,639 --> 00:05:07,560
is the stars and the sea.

64
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:10,600
You're sick.

65
00:05:14,160 --> 00:05:15,279
Let me introduce myself.

66
00:05:15,560 --> 00:05:16,319
Xu Kai.

67
00:05:16,480 --> 00:05:18,160
A big shot from Central Street.

68
00:05:18,639 --> 00:05:20,480
Madman is my business partner.

69
00:05:22,319 --> 00:05:22,800
Hello.

70
00:05:23,199 --> 00:05:24,040
I'm fine.

71
00:05:24,040 --> 00:05:24,959
But you're not.

72
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:26,199
You're sick.

73
00:05:27,959 --> 00:05:29,240
I... I'm sick?

74
00:05:29,519 --> 00:05:31,120
Hesitating when trouble comes,

75
00:05:31,360 --> 00:05:32,399
lacking courage—

76
00:05:32,639 --> 00:05:33,480
it's a sickness of the heart.

77
00:05:40,759 --> 00:05:41,319
Kid,

78
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:43,439
do you know the Madman of Central Street?

79
00:05:44,079 --> 00:05:44,639
Yes.

80
00:05:45,160 --> 00:05:46,319
He even kicked me once.

81
00:05:46,480 --> 00:05:47,079
It really hurt.

82
00:05:49,360 --> 00:05:50,000
How did he kick you?

83
00:05:50,319 --> 00:05:51,319
Like this.

84
00:05:51,519 --> 00:05:52,399
He kicked me flying.

85
00:05:56,439 --> 00:05:57,240
I didn't die, though.

86
00:06:00,639 --> 00:06:01,160
Sorry about that.

87
00:06:01,639 --> 00:06:02,279
You're not sick.

88
00:06:03,319 --> 00:06:04,040
I have things to do.

89
00:06:04,319 --> 00:06:04,759
Goodbye.

90
00:06:05,680 --> 00:06:06,319
Senior,

91
00:06:06,680 --> 00:06:08,199
my boss sent me to Black Street for training.

92
00:06:08,199 --> 00:06:09,000
Who should I look for?

93
00:06:19,639 --> 00:06:20,439
I understand.

94
00:06:23,959 --> 00:06:25,279
Who's the toughest on this street?

95
00:06:26,079 --> 00:06:26,759
I've got money.

96
00:06:27,120 --> 00:06:27,920
Lots of money.

97
00:06:30,560 --> 00:06:31,920
Who's the toughest on this street?

98
00:06:32,199 --> 00:06:33,000
I've got money.

99
00:06:33,279 --> 00:06:34,120
Lots of money.

100
00:06:34,800 --> 00:06:35,600
Who's the toughest on this street?

101
00:06:35,600 --> 00:06:36,519
What a rich mark.

102
00:06:36,639 --> 00:06:37,800
I've got money.

103
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:40,839
Know Madman, Cripple, and Fool?

104
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:41,600
I do.

105
00:06:42,079 --> 00:06:42,920
They're all formidable.

106
00:06:43,920 --> 00:06:46,120
All of them rose to power from here.

107
00:06:47,439 --> 00:06:48,600
So that would make them

108
00:06:48,800 --> 00:06:50,079
your senior disciples too.

109
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:53,040
If it weren't for your rare talent,

110
00:06:53,199 --> 00:06:54,519
forget ten thousand a day,

111
00:06:55,160 --> 00:06:57,040
I wouldn't take you for a million.

112
00:06:57,560 --> 00:06:58,199
Understood.

113
00:06:59,279 --> 00:06:59,839
We're here.

114
00:07:04,439 --> 00:07:07,000
Today, your first lesson from me is

115
00:07:07,839 --> 00:07:08,600
force control.

116
00:07:16,199 --> 00:07:17,199
Can you do it?

117
00:07:19,120 --> 00:07:19,800
Probably not.

118
00:07:28,959 --> 00:07:30,800
Force is easy to exert, hard to control.

119
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:32,839
The day you can

120
00:07:33,199 --> 00:07:35,160
make the stone slab

121
00:07:35,199 --> 00:07:36,920
crack but not shatter,

122
00:07:37,560 --> 00:07:38,600
that's when you've truly begun.

123
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:39,120
Right.

124
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:41,360
I still can't control my strength,

125
00:07:41,600 --> 00:07:42,519
like you do, Master,

126
00:07:43,120 --> 00:07:45,319
making the cracks so clear and even.

127
00:07:45,680 --> 00:07:46,519
Decent talent.

128
00:07:47,639 --> 00:07:48,399
Pity, though.

129
00:07:48,839 --> 00:07:50,519
Too rigid and forceful.

130
00:07:50,720 --> 00:07:51,720
Take your time practicing.

131
00:07:54,879 --> 00:07:55,519
Oh, right.

132
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:58,199
Don't forget to transfer the money.

133
00:07:58,519 --> 00:07:59,399
Tomorrow,

134
00:07:59,680 --> 00:08:01,680
give this courtyard a full cleaning.

135
00:08:02,199 --> 00:08:05,199
Tempering the mind matters too.

136
00:08:08,839 --> 00:08:09,639
Force control.

137
00:08:09,920 --> 00:08:10,680
Mind tempering.

138
00:08:11,639 --> 00:08:12,759
Such profound wisdom.

139
00:08:13,560 --> 00:08:15,920
Truly Black Street's top-secret camp.

140
00:08:16,800 --> 00:08:19,000
Just what kind of monster did I swindle?

141
00:08:19,120 --> 00:08:21,079
That was specially made marble!

142
00:08:21,560 --> 00:08:24,040
If he ever finds out I conned him,

143
00:08:25,040 --> 00:08:27,120
what if he tears me to pieces too?

144
00:08:35,039 --> 00:08:35,799
No.

145
00:08:38,159 --> 00:08:40,799
I'm Black Street's top con artist.

146
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:42,519
Fortune favors the bold.

147
00:08:57,799 --> 00:08:59,320
Is the Liu family that desperate for cash?

148
00:09:18,039 --> 00:09:18,639
Thank goodness,

149
00:09:19,639 --> 00:09:21,519
the ancient text on immortal spirits is still here.

150
00:09:24,399 --> 00:09:25,080
Just as I thought,

151
00:09:25,480 --> 00:09:26,519
the most dangerous place

152
00:09:27,360 --> 00:09:28,440
is the safest place.

153
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:31,799
Setting up the liaison post here again,

154
00:09:33,600 --> 00:09:35,960
even the Liu family would never guess

155
00:09:37,399 --> 00:09:38,840
that two shells

156
00:09:39,039 --> 00:09:40,559
would land in the same crater.

157
00:09:47,440 --> 00:09:49,159
Still, within the Liu family,

158
00:09:49,840 --> 00:09:51,480
I should recruit a few members.

159
00:09:53,480 --> 00:09:56,200
Otherwise I'd never feel at ease.

160
00:10:03,720 --> 00:10:04,440
Over here.

161
00:10:04,639 --> 00:10:05,440
Here, right here.

162
00:10:06,360 --> 00:10:07,879
Sorry, World's Strongest,

163
00:10:08,039 --> 00:10:08,960
mind if I interrupt?

164
00:10:10,120 --> 00:10:11,519
What made you think

165
00:10:11,519 --> 00:10:13,240
the Liu family are all fools

166
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:14,519
who don't know how to stake out a place?

167
00:10:15,840 --> 00:10:18,519
What was that you just dug up?

168
00:10:20,720 --> 00:10:21,399
I...

169
00:10:23,039 --> 00:10:24,120
I don't have anything.

170
00:10:24,279 --> 00:10:25,399
Then just kill him.

171
00:10:25,600 --> 00:10:26,679
He's of no more use.

172
00:10:27,000 --> 00:10:27,559
Got it.

173
00:10:28,600 --> 00:10:29,519
Wait, wait, wait!

174
00:10:41,039 --> 00:10:41,720
Let me go.

175
00:10:42,279 --> 00:10:43,080
The ancient text is yours.

176
00:10:43,159 --> 00:10:44,159
A wise choice.

177
00:10:44,679 --> 00:10:46,679
Looking forward to our next meeting.

178
00:10:47,480 --> 00:10:48,039
Bye-bye.

179
00:11:00,399 --> 00:11:02,279
He actually did come back.

180
00:11:03,279 --> 00:11:03,879
Hey,

181
00:11:04,039 --> 00:11:05,639
bring the stuff back here quickly.

182
00:11:05,840 --> 00:11:06,480
Also,

183
00:11:06,879 --> 00:11:08,080
the most important thing

184
00:11:08,240 --> 00:11:09,000
is this:

185
00:11:09,200 --> 00:11:11,039
He probably won't come back here again.

186
00:11:11,320 --> 00:11:13,279
Just leave one camera.

187
00:11:13,720 --> 00:11:15,120
Dismantle all the rest.

188
00:11:15,240 --> 00:11:16,240
Take them to Digital Street.

189
00:11:16,399 --> 00:11:17,559
Sell them to anyone who pays.

190
00:11:17,919 --> 00:11:19,679
Then bring the money to my office.

191
00:11:19,679 --> 00:11:20,320
You hear me?

192
00:11:21,399 --> 00:11:22,159
Got it.

193
00:11:23,440 --> 00:11:24,200
It's really important.

194
00:11:24,200 --> 00:11:24,879
Really important.

195
00:11:26,240 --> 00:11:27,799
You two, go dismantle them.

196
00:11:32,559 --> 00:11:33,320
Awesome!

197
00:11:33,720 --> 00:11:35,000
Next month's allowance

198
00:11:35,279 --> 00:11:36,399
is sorted now.

199
00:11:39,759 --> 00:11:41,559
Wang Qiusheng, oh Wang Qiusheng.

200
00:11:42,039 --> 00:11:43,039
I can always count on you.

201
00:11:43,600 --> 00:11:45,440
What would I do without you?

202
00:11:46,519 --> 00:11:47,240
Where you going?

203
00:11:48,440 --> 00:11:50,080
I'm heading out

204
00:11:50,840 --> 00:11:51,600
for a little walk.

205
00:11:52,080 --> 00:11:52,799
Alright.

206
00:11:53,679 --> 00:11:54,559
I heard

207
00:11:54,720 --> 00:11:57,559
there's cash from the scrapped cameras

208
00:11:57,639 --> 00:11:58,759
that'll end up in your hands.

209
00:11:59,120 --> 00:12:00,559
Remember to bring it back tomorrow.

210
00:12:00,759 --> 00:12:01,360
Father.

211
00:12:01,759 --> 00:12:02,799
Father,

212
00:12:04,600 --> 00:12:06,399
are we short on money?

213
00:12:06,440 --> 00:12:07,120
Short on money?

214
00:12:08,639 --> 00:12:10,600
How could our family be short on money?

215
00:12:11,000 --> 00:12:13,320
Look at our family's big company.

216
00:12:13,440 --> 00:12:14,720
It's not short on cash.

217
00:12:14,720 --> 00:12:16,720
So why do you keep shortchanging me?

218
00:12:17,240 --> 00:12:17,840
Other people

219
00:12:18,039 --> 00:12:19,679
get to drink Qiushui coffee freely.

220
00:12:19,879 --> 00:12:20,799
But when it comes to me...

221
00:12:20,799 --> 00:12:21,720
This guy's incredible.

222
00:12:21,720 --> 00:12:22,600
We won!

223
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:25,960
What did you just say?

224
00:12:27,600 --> 00:12:28,360
I said,

225
00:12:28,360 --> 00:12:29,240
I just remembered.

226
00:12:29,440 --> 00:12:31,519
Raise boys poor, raise girls rich.

227
00:12:32,480 --> 00:12:33,919
That old man from Qiushui City

228
00:12:34,919 --> 00:12:37,120
told me that very seriously.

229
00:12:37,919 --> 00:12:38,759
Look at us now.

230
00:12:39,120 --> 00:12:40,799
It proves he was right.

231
00:12:44,159 --> 00:12:47,960
The pro agreed to add me as a friend!

232
00:12:50,320 --> 00:12:51,960
I'll send you a few skins first.

233
00:12:52,120 --> 00:12:53,279
So you can carry me.

234
00:12:54,759 --> 00:12:56,960
Bro, you're amazing!

235
00:13:00,320 --> 00:13:02,080
That old geezer is quite something too.

236
00:13:02,840 --> 00:13:05,440
Dresses his own son in gold and silver,

237
00:13:05,840 --> 00:13:07,519
fattens him up like a pig,

238
00:13:08,120 --> 00:13:10,480
then tricks my dad into mistreating me?

239
00:13:11,039 --> 00:13:12,240
What a scumbag.

240
00:13:23,679 --> 00:13:24,240
Tongtong.

241
00:13:24,759 --> 00:13:25,559
Do you need help?

242
00:13:36,080 --> 00:13:37,360
In her current condition,

243
00:13:37,840 --> 00:13:39,240
even the Rat's celestial seed

244
00:13:39,639 --> 00:13:41,320
can only ease the symptoms now?

245
00:13:44,600 --> 00:13:45,559
Time is running out.

246
00:13:46,440 --> 00:13:48,360
Where can I find another immortal?

247
00:13:49,200 --> 00:13:50,320
A true immortal.

248
00:13:57,440 --> 00:13:58,200
Watch over her for me.

249
00:14:12,159 --> 00:14:12,879
Why

250
00:14:13,279 --> 00:14:14,559
is your celestial seed withered?

251
00:14:15,200 --> 00:14:16,000
Speak!

252
00:14:25,720 --> 00:14:28,080
Where on earth can I find a good celestial seed?
